      • RTypeInstruction

        public RTypeInstruction()
        The default constructor for the RTypeInstruction. It should be followed by initialization of all of the fields of the instruction.

      • RTypeInstruction

        public RTypeInstruction(java.lang.String opc,
                int rd,
                int rs,
                int rt,
                int shamt,
                int funct,
                int seqnum)
        The primary constructor for the RTypeInsturction. It includes all fields of the instruction in the order in which they appear in the assembly code.
        Parameters:
        opc - The opcode for the instruction.
        rd - The destination register for the instruction.
        rs - The source register for the instruction.
        rt - The third register for the instruction.
        shamt - The shift amount for the instruction.
        funct - The function code for the instruction.
